                        },
                        {
                            Name: "I need to prepare",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You read the board too. Greenspace 7, under-performing. This garden fed three generations of trainers before their comparator was a drawing. Let them measure. I am not moving."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "They sent a man with a clipboard because a bulldozer would photograph badly. The garden bends. It does not break. Neither do I. Now — did you come to talk zoning, or to battle?"
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Blossom — the paperwork",
                    Label: "notice_seen"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "defeated_hua_zhan_leader"
                        },
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "defeated_villain_yield_analyst"
                        }
                    ],
                    Priority: 26,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Grow well, Leader",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The analyst refiled my garden this morning. Brand asset, heritage class, retained. Saved by foot traffic. I wanted to be angry. But the garden does not ask why the rain comes, and perhaps I should learn from it."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "You beat him at his own arithmetic and the badge crowd did the rest. The numbers now say the garden earns. It was always earning. They simply could not read the currency."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Blossom — retained",
                    Label: "retained_after"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "pilgrimage_done"
                        }
                    ],
                    Priority: 16,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Challenge the Gym",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    Conditions: [
