                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    Conditions: [
                                        {
                                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                                            Name: "no_defeated_hua_zhan_leader"
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    Cmd: "tbcs battle GEN_9_SINGLES @s vs hua_zhan_leader onwin {1: ['cobbledollars give @1 1800', 'tag @1 add defeated_hua_zhan_leader', '@2 say Good roots. You bend where you must and you hold where it counts. Go on growing.'], 2: ['@1 say A seedling cannot rush the sun. Tend your team and come back when you have grown.']}"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "yes_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "I need to prepare",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Four seals and the smell of the moss court still on your sleeves. Master Wei does not send many pilgrims down the hill — the old way asks more patience than most challengers carry."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The gardens already taught you what I would have: grass does not win by force. It outlasts. Show me what the hill grew, pilgrim — the Bloom Badge is waiting."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Blossom — the pilgrim",
                    Label: "pilgrim"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "defeated_hua_zhan_leader"
                        }
                    ],
                    Priority: 20,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Thank you, Leader",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The Bloom Badge suits you. You learned the lesson most trainers trample right past: a thing that bends does not break."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Be careful in the wheat country north of here. The fields used to belong to the farmers. Now they belong to people in grey who never get their boots dirty."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Blossom — after defeat",
                    Label: "after"
                },
                {
                    Priority: 10,
                    Buttons: [
